manifest.name: Onyx Boox Annotation & Highlight Extractor
manifest.description: This plugin extracts annotations and highlights files exported from Onyx Boox tablets, and converts them to reference, literature and permanent notes fitting to the Zettelkasten method.
manifest.author: Akos Balasko
